{"logo":"https://ss0.bdstatic.com/9bA1vGfa2gU2pMbfm9GUKT-w/timg?wisealaddin&size=8&quality=60&sec=1534502968&di=936d598f8425f85d06fdb2d84a75e806&src=http%3A%2F%2Ff.hiphotos.baidu.com%2Fxiaodu%2Fpic%2Fitem%2F0df431adcbef7609869333b326dda3cc7cd99e06.jpg","summary":"湖南科技学院(Hunan University of Science and Engineering)，坐落于素有“锦绣潇湘”之称的著名历史文化名城“竹城”——永州，是湖南永州市的最高学府，是湖南省“十三五”硕士学位授予单位立项建设单位(第三批)。该校创建于1941年，前身为湖南省立第七师范学校，1971年创办专科教育，2002年由原零陵师范高等专科学校升格为本科院校——零陵学院，2004年更名为湖南科技学院。截至2018年1月，学校建有13个教学学院，43个普通本科专业，面向全国28个省(市、区)招生。现有普通本科在校学生14810人，成人教育在校学生5000余人。现有教职员工近1100人。学校占地面积76.3万平方米，建筑面积45万平方米，教学仪器设备总值1.4亿元，图书资料107万册，固定资产总值7.3亿元。","tags":["理工类","本科","公办"],"attrs":{"创建时间":"1971","所在地区":"湖南省永州市零陵区杨梓塘路130号","院校隶属":"湖南省教育厅"},"imgs":["https://ss0.bdstatic.com/9bA1vGfa2gU2pMbfm9GUKT-w/timg?wisealaddin&size=f300_300&quality=60&sec=1534502968&di=4d988b8c714247296bc2f03a2085afab&src=http%3A%2F%2Ft10.baidu.com%2Fit%2Fu%3D3558994245%2C3926236555%26fm%3D179%26w%3D300%26h%3D300%26img.JPEG","https://ss0.bdstatic.com/9bA1vGfa2gU2pMbfm9GUKT-w/timg?wisealaddin&size=f300_300&quality=60&sec=1534502968&di=6f613ee08339c55fe8e55d282c9d2f27&src=http%3A%2F%2Ft11.baidu.com%2Fit%2Fu%3D2879816248%2C2825588796%26fm%3D179%26w%3D300%26h%3D300%26img.JPEG","https://ss0.bdstatic.com/9bA1vGfa2gU2pMbfm9GUKT-w/timg?wisealaddin&size=f300_300&quality=60&sec=1534502968&di=47a7cd08e31ee8847636024b1b384a80&src=http%3A%2F%2Ft12.baidu.com%2Fit%2Fu%3D3623786861%2C911931848%26fm%3D179%26w%3D300%26h%3D300%26img.JPEG","https://ss0.bdstatic.com/9bA1vGfa2gU2pMbfm9GUKT-w/timg?wisealaddin&size=f300_300&quality=60&sec=1534502968&di=b4aa55f0154327fec042d9532592d586&src=http%3A%2F%2Ft12.baidu.com%2Fit%2Fu%3D3651017789%2C791433048%26fm%3D179%26w%3D300%26h%3D300%26img.JPEG","https://ss0.bdstatic.com/9bA1vGfa2gU2pMbfm9GUKT-w/timg?wisealaddin&size=f300_300&quality=60&sec=1534502968&di=04ff173e068b41c6a1ac5851564c4c1f&src=http%3A%2F%2Ft11.baidu.com%2Fit%2Fu%3D3459326752%2C3957948192%26fm%3D179%26w%3D300%26h%3D300%26img.JPEG","https://